OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA mostly dry
OL,6,Fevening and night with plenty of clear
OL,7,Fspells. Some low cloud developing over
OL,8,Fthe hills during the early hours with
OL,9,Fthe odd spot of rain. Staying mild.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FA fresher feeling day with
OL,12,Fplenty of bright or sunny spells,
OL,13,Fespecially through the afternoon.
OL,14,FBreezy along the coast and over the
OL,15,Fhills.
